{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was in a good, cheerful mood-- apart from the fact that we had already five or six people who were dead, the elderly people, I mean, the-- [? all the-- ?] I mean, they-- they couldn't take the heat, they couldn't take to be without food for-- for three, four days, and they died.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people were unconscious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the older people suffered terribly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But 20, 21 year old, we thought it's a great adventure, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See what will happen next.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we still had some bread in the rucksacks, so we could eat something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not much, but we had some bread, and even couple of bites of sausage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the next day, in the morning, then we-- the train stopped, and we looked out and just realized it was a strange town.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in my background was a huge sign saying, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never heard about the word 'Auschwitz.' Nobody ever told us that such a place exists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's some Polish or German town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then all the doors swung open, and [LAUGHS] then all hell broke loose in one second.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here there they were, about two dozen SS men with their savage dogs-- all the dogs barking at once, jumping, trying to jump at us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the-- the kapos, the-- in the striped uniforms, who were-- some of them were Jewish, most of them were not Jewish-- German criminals who were-- who were also prisoners.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They jumped at us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERAMN] Out, out!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody out!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Leave the luggage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Leave everything behind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No need to bring the suitcases or luggage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That will be transported later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Leave everything there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You get it later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody jumped.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
